parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the Auto Start/Stop system can cause the vehicle to shut off unexpectedly, leading to a loss of power and control, which can increase the risk of accidents, especially when driving in heavy traffic or at intersections.
symptoms: The vehicle shuts off unexpectedly
the engine fails to restart
the vehicle will not turn back on
the instrument cluster lights flash
the vehicle is unable to shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the instrument cluster display can cause critical information, such as speed, fuel level, and warning lights, to be obscured or invisible, which can increase the risk of accidents, especially when driving at high speeds or in hazardous conditions.
symptoms: The instrument cluster display is dim or invisible
the display is stuck in night mode
the display is unresponsive to brightness adjustments
the display is difficult to see in daylight.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause various safety features, such as forward collision warning, lane departure warning, and automatic emergency braking, to malfunction or fail, which can increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The forward collision warning
lane departure warning
and automatic emergency braking systems malfunction or fail
the infotainment system flashes or fails to load
the vehicle's safety features turn themselves off.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the instrument cluster display can cause the driver to be distracted from the driving task, leading to accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: The display is too bright or too dim
making it difficult to read the speedometer
fuel gauge
and other important information; the display does not adjust to daylight or nighttime conditions; the display is stuck in day or night mode; the display is not visible during daylight hours.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the auto-dim feature can cause the driver to be distracted from the driving task, leading to accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: The display does not dim automatically in response to changes in ambient light; the display is stuck in bright mode; the display is not adjustable manually; the display causes glare or night blindness.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission and shifting system can cause the vehicle to stall, hard shift, or become difficult to shift, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
the clutch pedal sticks to the floor
the clutch pedal does not return to its normal position
the clutch pedal has a delayed return to its normal position
the clutch pedal has a sudden loss of pressure
the vehicle is unable to shift into gear
hard shifting
stalling.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the backup camera can cause the driver to be unable to see behind the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The backup camera screen is extremely dark or black
especially at night.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the display and instrument panel can cause the driver to be unable to see important information, such as speed, warnings, and temperature, which can lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The digital dashboard display appears dim or stuck in night mode
the display is unable to be seen in daylight
warnings and information are not displayed.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical and auto start/stop system can cause the vehicle to stall, shut off, or become difficult to restart, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or shuts off
especially when stopping or accelerating
the auto start/stop system fails to restart the vehicle
the emergency parking light and check engine light turn on.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake system can cause the vehicle to be difficult to stop, which can lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle makes strange noises
especially when braking
the brakes seem to be malfunctioning.
